      "content": "sitting in the sun... i don't even know why i bother with things like that. it feels like i'm just performing for a world that doesn't matter anymore. if the weight never goes away, why am i even being forced to keep carrying it? it feels like the only way to actually find that peace you're talking about is to just... stop fighting it.",
